title: The Straight Pipes' Yuri & Jakub
description:
Yuri and Jakub are a duo from Canada who run the YouTube channel, The Straight Pipes. They do car reviews, comparisons, and look at the new tech in cars. 


Watch the Straight Pipes: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC86SBFIAgnYL3ll2ZDgmsuA

This show is available as a video! https://youtu.be/H9ZisUEZ73M
